{"type": "article", "id": 7692, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-03-24T08:46:21Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 2559, "name": "花瓶"}, {"id": 266, "name": "椅子"}, {"id": 1130, "name": "手表"}, {"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702102207FUMSgIqkvV8auANb.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tDefender by Paul Smith &amp; Land Rover\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\tLand Rover 此前宣布将会在其 70 周年之际推出全新的 Defender 车系，最近他们联手英国时尚品牌 Paul Smith 送 Defender “最后一程”，推出了一款定制版 Defender，Paul Smith 手下的车身外观具备调色盘式的设计风格，选取了 27 种不同配色，且融入 Smith 经典的彩条元素。更有趣的是车顶的一只手绘大黄蜂，看上去动感又幽默。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102155a62Thl03UKsxSyVX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102155WbCnlwxZ3BXf27Fd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021021563p0ekEYwXhNVurxv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102156JDxeSc0FW6I4Epli.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021021573yM9CYPjXkzq5aow.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102157Qb0it6YncWANXgL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66628702\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t Timeburner by Miki Eleta\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t在瑞士举办的 Baselworld 手表珠宝展览会上，Miki Eleta 带来了他的作品，这款名为 Timeburner 的运动手表。这款手表的设计灵感来自于摩托车的发动机，是对早期内燃机的致敬：铝制的活塞代替了指针，机械运动驱动活塞，推动着齿轮旋转，同时又指示着秒数。这款手表每一款都限量生产，只有 99 个，三种颜色可选，分别是银白色 （silverlight）、铬黄骑士色（chrome-rider）和全黑色（all-black）。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102157GXuzMrLaTxZfhoOd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102158oQjcIGMU1Ydlhxae.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74572127\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102158A0fsleuJCh2BQ9TM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.75061125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102159qvIf8EWACG32dyr1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.73716381\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tJosie Chair by Mathery Studio\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\tMathery Studio 设计的这款椅子是一款“会开玩笑”的椅子，椅子背上的绳子上面连接彩色滑轮，下面被绑在了一个微微倾斜的表面，形成喷射时的张力。当人坐在上面的时候，椅子座位表面承受到压力，塑料滑轮中便会喷出五彩缤纷的彩带。其设计灵感来自上个世纪末的一部电影《一吻定江山》，其中的女主角由于无法融入社交圈中被其他孩子取笑，并且给她取外号为 Josie Grossie，这个女孩即使聚会也是一个人坐在椅子上。Mathery Studio 以此为灵感，让她的椅子变得生动有趣起来，于是便设计了这一款椅子。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102159yLQ0vcqi5mY2kKAh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.96943765\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102159HqyvPBTxQ4KDsw01.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.42787286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102200k7nRIPqdrhweEm36.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.10635697\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022002b9cTFMwf4KCWpRx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77261614\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102201L2T9SxkEcNBipbVf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.81784841\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102201ywfpVGEMJD7LjY3c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102202IX1PfVtHyW9e5gAC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.700489\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102202os5WrPFVIGHtv7bl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71149144\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tWald by Feltmark\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t来自洛杉矶的设计工作室 Feltmark 推出的这一款立灯采用的是极简主义设计风格，他们省去了一切不必要的装饰，仅仅保留了立灯最原始和重要的部分：发光体和电源。电源暴露在外面，可以直接被插入插座中，而铝制的灯杆经过一系列复杂的加工程序，耐用，精致并且优雅。这款产品有两种尺寸：大号的安装后有四尺高，小号有三尺高。目前产品售价为 139 美元，<a href=\"http://feltmark.com/collections/wald\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102202RNvxulWrkFiydL62.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.68337408\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102203G2Am8K1p75RcsXEz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.20660147\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022036hiWgoZxcr9QjPGB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102203Op9e7cfFtnMEqgyY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102204YL4VJt8XFgN3DylS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102204QZ8zGCTyc6iEaIwb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022042jBteLYxI8Oof1Km.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022058hZPSH3zITdkRu9U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60391198\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\t Eva Transformable Shoes by Factotum &amp; Fobs\r\n</h2>\r\n<p>\r\n\tEva 向来被评为是动漫史上最能圈钱的作品，他们 20 周年庆祝活动推出了一系列的“烧钱”计划，前不久的“<span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\">朗基努斯枪插入月球”系列激励了众多土豪们，而最近他们又推出了一个系列的纪念篮球鞋。这款鞋由 Eva 和<span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\">日本的 FACTOTUM 品牌，协同球鞋厂 Fobs 的合作设计，有“创刊号机”、“零号机”、“2 号机”、“Mark.用旅游鞋再现06”四种不同的选择。目前定价为 33000 日元（约人民币 1699 元），这里是<a href=\"http://radio-eva.jp/special/2015/0318-7087.php\" target=\"_blank\">购买链接</a>，Eva 真粉们可以上了。</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022052Jc9EyHQGZ7nouMg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102206ObqpAjEYfyKc6gNv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56203704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022069lscPetpv0oZwm3S.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016070210220614BYJlZISTMXqa9z.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.57314815\" data-format=\"jpeg\"></span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><span style=\"color:#5E5D5D;font-family:fontello, icomoon, tmt-icons, topbar, sv, MD_Font, octicons, 'Glyphicons Halflings', FontAwesome, dashicons, iconfont, 'Segoe UI', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei Mono', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'Microsoft Yahei Mono', ，, 微软雅黑, sans-serif;font-size:14px;letter-spacing:1px;line-height:24px;white-space:normal;\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102207pN4DRSe5PU30J9Zv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n"}